long_description: engineering the skies since 2002. regulus group has been partnering with the faa and the aviation community for over 15 years to solve complex problems with creative, high-caliber, and cost-effective services. we have an outstanding talent base with an unparalleled level of engineering expertise, air traffic operations knowledge, and program management experience. this depth of experience integrated with a broad set of program management, finance, and operations research capabilities has enabled regulus to become the premier systems engineering and program management services provider for the faa's most challenging programs. regulus' integrated service offerings enable collaboration across critical disciplines & with key stakeholders, which allows our customers to maintain an enterprise perspective while program planning and execution continue in a coordinated and effective manner. regulus values customer engagement and being close to our customers allows us to be responsive. we have four main offices in washington, dc, virginia, new jersey, and oklahoma.
